      "prompt": "请创建一个完整的 HTML5 游戏。游戏描述：可以穿墙、这边进那边出。\n                    \n重要技术要求：\n1. 单个 HTML 文件\n2. 使用 Canvas API\n3. Canvas 尺寸必须为 360x640 像素（9:16 竖屏比例）\n4. 在 JavaScript 中设置：canvas.width = 360; canvas.height = 640;\n5. 在 CSS 中设置：canvas { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; margin: 0 auto; }\n6. 包含完整游戏循环\n7. 有得分系统\n8. 确保有趣可玩\n\n只返回 HTML 代码，不要其他说明。",
      "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>穿墙迷宫</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n        \n        body {\n            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);\n            min-height: 100vh;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n        \n        .game-container {\n            position: relative;\n            width: 360px;\n            max-width: 100%;\n        }\n        \n        canvas {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            display: block;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n            background: #0f0f23;\n        }\n        \n        .ui-overlay {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            pointer-events: none;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n        \n        .score-display {\n            text-align: center;\n            color: white;\n            font-size: 24px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n        \n        .score-value {\n            color: #4fd1c5;\n            font-size: 32px;\n        }\n        \n        .high-score {\n            color: #ffd700;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            margin-top: 5px;\n        }\n        \n        .controls {\n            text-align: center;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);\n            font-size: 14px;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n        \n        .menu-screen, .game-over-screen, .pause-screen {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            color: white;\n            pointer-events: auto;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            opacity: 0;\n            transition: opacity 0.3s;\n        }\n        \n        .menu-screen.active, .game-over-screen.active, .pause-screen.active {\n            opacity: 1;\n        }\n        \n        .menu-title {\n            font-size: 36px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: #4fd1c5;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(79, 209, 197, 0.5);\n        }\n        \n        .menu-subtitle {\n            font-size: 18px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\n        }\n        \n        .game-button {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4fd1c5 0%, #38b2ac 100%);\n            color: white;\n            border: none;\n            padding: 12px 30px;\n            margin: 10px;\n            border-radius: 25px;\n            font-size: 18px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: all 0.3s;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(79, 209, 197, 0.3);\n            pointer-events: auto;\n        }\n        \n        .game-button:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(79, 209, 197, 0.4);\n        }\n        \n        .game-button:active {\n            transform: translateY(0);\n        }\n        \n        .instructions {\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\n            font-size: 14px;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        \n        .final-score {\n            font-size: 48px;\n            color: #4fd1c5;\n            margin: 20px 0;\n        }\n        \n        .game-over-title {\n            font-size: 32px;\n            color: #ff6b6b;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"game-container\">\n        <canvas id=\"gameCanvas\" width=\"360\" height=\"640\"></canvas>\n        \n        <div class=\"ui-overlay\">\n            <div class=\"score-display\">\n                <div>得分: <span class=\"score-value\" id=\"score\">0</span></div>\n                <div class=\"high-score\">最高分: <span id=\"highScore\">0</span></div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"controls\">\n                方向键或WASD移动 | P暂停 | 穿墙逃脱敌人！\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"menu-screen active\" id=\"menuScreen\">\n            <h1 class=\"menu-title\">穿墙迷宫</h1>\n            <div class=\"menu-subtitle\">收集能量球，躲避敌人！</div>\n            <button class=\"game-button\" id=\"startButton\">开始游戏</button>\n            <div class=\"instructions\">\n                <p>🎮 方向键或WASD控制移动</p>\n                <p>🌀 穿过墙壁从另一边出现</p>\n                <p>⭐ 收集绿色能量球得分</p>\n                <p>💀 躲避红色敌人</p>\n                <p>⏸️ 按P键暂停游戏</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"game-over-screen\" id=\"gameOverScreen\">\n            <div class=\"game-over-title\">游戏结束</div>\n            <div class=\"final-score\" id=\"finalScore\">0</div>\n            <button class=\"game-button\" id=\"restartButton\">重新开始</button>\n            <button class=\"game-button\" id=\"menuButton\">返回菜单</button>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"pause-screen\" id=\"pauseScreen\">\n            <div class=\"menu-title\">游戏暂停</div>\n            <button class=\"game-button\" id=\"resumeButton\">继续游戏</button>\n            <button class=\"game-button\" id=\"pauseMenuButton\">返回菜单</button>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        // 游戏常量\n        const CANVAS_WIDTH = 360;\n        const CANVAS_HEIGHT = 640;\n        const PLAYER_SIZE = 20;\n        const ENERGY_SIZE = 15;\n        const ENEMY_SIZE = 18;\n        const PLAYER_SPEED = 5;\n        const ENEMY_SPEED = 2;\n        const ENERGY_COUNT = 5;\n        const ENEMY_COUNT = 3;\n        \n        // 游戏状态\n        const GameState = {\n            MENU: 'menu',\n            PLAYING: 'playing',\n            PAUSED: 'paused',\n            GAME_OVER: 'gameover'\n        };\n        \n        // 游戏变量\n        let canvas, ctx;\n        let gameState = GameState.MENU;\n        let score = 0;\n        let highScore = 0;\n        let lastTime = 0;\n        \n        // 游戏对象\n        let player = {\n            x: CANVAS_WIDTH / 2,\n            y: CANVAS_HEIGHT / 2,\n            dx: 0,\n            dy: 0,\n            size: PLAYER_SIZE,\n            color: '#4fd1c5'\n        };\n        \n        let energies = [];\n        let enemies = [];\n        \n        // 输入状态\n        let keys = {\n            up: false,\n            down: false,\n            left: false,\n            right: false\n        };\n        \n        // 初始化游戏\n        function init() {\n            canvas = document.getElementById('gameCanvas');\n            ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');\n            \n            // 设置画布尺寸\n            canvas.width = CANVAS_WIDTH;\n            canvas.height = CANVAS_HEIGHT;\n            \n            // 加载最高分\n            highScore = parseInt(localStorage.getItem('wallPasserHighScore')) || 0;\n            document.getElementById('highScore').textContent = highScore;\n            \n            // 设置事件监听\n            setupEventListeners();\n            \n            // 开始游戏循环\n            requestAnimationFrame(gameLoop);\n        }\n        \n        // 设置事件监听\n        function setupEventListeners() {\n            // 键盘事件\n            document.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {\n                handleInput(e.key, true);\n            });\n            \n            document.addEventListener('keyup', (e) => {\n                handleInput(e.key, false);\n            });\n            \n            // 按钮事件\n            document.getElementById('startButton').addEventListener('click', startGame);\n            document.getElementById('restartButton').addEventListener('click', startGame);\n            document.getElementById('menuButton').addEventListener('click', showMenu);\n            document.getElementById('resumeButton').addEventListener('click', resumeGame);\n            document.getElementById('pauseMenuButton').addEventListener('click', showMenu);\n        }\n        \n        // 处理输入\n        function handleInput(key, pressed) {\n            switch(key.toLowerCase()) {\n                case 'arrowup':\n                case 'w':\n                    keys.up = pressed;\n                    break;\n                case 'arrowdown':\n                case 's':\n                    keys.down = pressed;\n                    break;\n                case 'arrowleft':\n                case 'a':\n                    keys.left = pressed;\n                    break;\n                case 'arrowright':\n                case 'd':\n                    keys.right = pressed;\n                    break;\n                case 'p':\n                    if (pressed && gameState === GameState.PLAYING) {\n                        pauseGame();\n                    } else if (pressed && gameState === GameState.PAUSED) {\n                        resumeGame();\n                    }\n                    break;\n                case ' ':\n                    if (pressed && gameState === GameState.MENU) {\n                        startGame();\n                    }\n                    break;\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 开始游戏\n        function startGame() {\n            gameState = GameState.PLAYING;\n            score = 0;\n            document.getElementById('score').textContent = score;\n            \n            // 重置玩家位置\n            player.x = CANVAS_WIDTH / 2;\n            player.y = CANVAS_HEIGHT / 2;\n            player.dx = 0;\n            player.dy = 0;\n            \n            // 生成能量球\n            energies = [];\n            for (let i = 0; i < ENERGY_COUNT; i++) {\n                spawnEnergy();\n            }\n            \n            // 生成敌人\n            enemies = [];\n            for (let i = 0; i < ENEMY_COUNT; i++) {\n                spawnEnemy();\n            }\n            \n            // 隐藏菜单，显示游戏\n            document.getElementById('menuScreen').classList.remove('active');\n            document.getElementById('gameOverScreen').classList.remove('active');\n            document.getElementById('pauseScreen').classList.remove('active');\n        }\n        \n        // 暂停游戏\n        function pauseGame() {\n            gameState = GameState.PAUSED;\n            document.getElementById('pauseScreen').classList.add('active');\n        }\n        \n        // 恢复游戏\n        function resumeGame() {\n            gameState = GameState.PLAYING;\n            document.getElementById('pauseScreen').classList.remove('active');\n        }\n        \n        // 显示菜单\n        function showMenu() {\n            gameState = GameState.MENU;\n            document.getElementById('menuScreen').classList.add('active');\n            document.getElementById('gameOverScreen').classList.remove('active');\n            document.getElementById('pauseScreen').classList.remove('active');\n        }\n        \n        // 游戏结束\n        function gameOver() {\n            gameState = GameState.GAME_OVER;\n            \n            // 更新最高分\n            if (score > highScore) {\n                highScore = score;\n                localStorage.setItem('wallPasserHighScore', highScore);\n                document.getElementById('highScore').textContent = highScore;\n            }\n            \n            document.getElementById('finalScore').textContent = score;\n            document.getElementById('gameOverScreen').classList.add('active');\n        }\n        \n        // 生成能量球\n        function spawnEnergy() {\n            energies.push({\n                x: Math.random() * (CANVAS_WIDTH - ENERGY_SIZE * 2) + ENERGY_SIZE,\n                y: Math.random() * (CANVAS_HEIGHT - ENERGY_SIZE * 2) + ENERGY_SIZE,\n                size: ENERGY_SIZE,\n                color: '#4ade80',\n                pulse: 0\n            });\n        }\n        \n        // 生成敌人\n        function spawnEnemy() {\n            let x, y;\n            \n            // 确保敌人不会在玩家附近生成\n            do {\n                x = Math.random() * (CANVAS_WIDTH - ENEMY_SIZE * 2) + ENEMY_SIZE;\n                y = Math.random() * (CANVAS_HEIGHT - ENEMY_SIZE * 2) + ENEMY_SIZE;\n            } while (Math.abs(x - player.x) < 100 && Math.abs(y - player.y) < 100);\n            \n            enemies.push({\n                x: x,\n                y: y,\n                dx: (Math.random() > 0.5 ? 1 : -1) * ENEMY_SPEED,\n                dy: (Math.random() > 0.5 ? 1 : -1) * ENEMY_SPEED,\n                size: ENEMY_SIZE,\n                color: '#ff6b6b'\n            });\n        }\n        \n        // 更新游戏逻辑\n        function update(deltaTime) {\n            if (gameState !== GameState.PLAYING) return;\n            \n            // 更新玩家速度\n            player.dx = 0;\n            player.dy = 0;\n            \n            if (keys.up) player.dy = -PLAYER_SPEED;\n            if (keys.down) player.dy = PLAYER_SPEED;\n            if (keys.left) player.dx = -PLAYER_SPEED;\n            if (keys.right) player.dx = PLAYER_SPEED;\n            \n            // 更新玩家位置（穿墙逻辑）\n            player.x += player.dx;\n            player.y += player.dy;\n            \n            // 穿墙处理\n            if (player.x < -player.size) player.x = CANVAS_WIDTH + player.size;\n            if (player.x > CANVAS_WIDTH + player.size) player.x = -player.size;\n            if (player.y < -player.size) player.y = CANVAS_HEIGHT + player.size;\n            if (player.y > CANVAS_HEIGHT + player.size) player.y = -player.size;\n            \n            // 更新能量球脉冲效果\n            energies.forEach(energy => {\n                energy.pulse = (energy.pulse + 0.05) % (Math.PI * 2);\n            });\n            \n            // 更新敌人位置（穿墙逻辑）\n            enemies.forEach(enemy => {\n                enemy.x += enemy.dx;\n                enemy.y += enemy.dy;\n                \n                // 穿墙处理\n                if (enemy.x < -enemy.size) enemy.x = CANVAS_WIDTH + enemy.size;\n                if (enemy.x > CANVAS_WIDTH + enemy.size) enemy.x = -enemy.size;\n                if (enemy.y < -enemy.size) enemy.y = CANVAS_HEIGHT + enemy.size;\n                if (enemy.y > CANVAS_HEIGHT + enemy.size) enemy.y = -enemy.size;\n            });\n            \n            // 检测玩家与能量球的碰撞\n            for (let i = energies.length - 1; i >= 0; i--) {\n                const energy = energies[i];\n                const distance = Math.sqrt(\n                    Math.pow(player.x - energy.x, 2) + \n                    Math.pow(player.y - energy.y, 2)\n                );\n                \n                if (distance < player.size + energy.size) {\n                    // 收集能量球\n                    score += 10;\n                    document.getElementById('score').textContent = score;\n                    \n                    // 移除能量球并生成新的\n                    energies.splice(i, 1);\n                    spawnEnergy();\n                }\n            }\n            \n            // 检测玩家与敌人的碰撞\n            for (let i = 0; i < enemies.length; i++) {\n                const enemy = enemies[i];\n                const distance = Math.sqrt(\n                    Math.pow(player.x - enemy.x, 2) + \n                    Math.pow(player.y - enemy.y, 2)\n                );\n                \n                if (distance < player.size + enemy.size) {\n                    gameOver();\n                    return;\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 渲染游戏\n        function render() {\n            // 清空画布\n            ctx.fillStyle = '#0f0f23';\n            ctx.fillRect(0, 0, CANVAS_WIDTH, CANVAS_HEIGHT);\n            \n            // 绘制网格背景\n            ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(79, 209, 197, 0.1)';\n            ctx.lineWidth = 1;\n            \n            for (let x = 0; x <= CANVAS_WIDTH; x += 40) {\n                ctx.beginPath();\n                ctx.moveTo(x, 0);\n                ctx.lineTo(x, CANVAS_HEIGHT);\n                ctx.stroke();\n            }\n            \n            for (let y = 0; y <= CANVAS_HEIGHT; y += 40) {\n                ctx.beginPath();\n                ctx.moveTo(0, y);\n                ctx.lineTo(CANVAS_WIDTH, y);\n                ctx.stroke();\n            }\n            \n            // 绘制能量球\n            energies.forEach(energy => {\n                const pulseSize = energy.size + Math.sin(energy.pulse) * 3;\n                \n                // 绘制光晕\n                ctx.beginPath();\n                ctx.arc(energy.x, energy.y, pulseSize + 5, 0, Math.PI * 2);\n                ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.2)';\n                ctx.fill();\n                \n                // 绘制能量球\n                ctx.beginPath();\n                ctx.arc(energy.x, energy.y, pulseSize, 0, Math.PI * 2);\n                ctx.fillStyle = energy.color;\n                ctx.fill();\n                \n                // 绘制高光\n                ctx.beginPath();\n                ctx.arc(energy.x - pulseSize/3, energy.y - pulseSize/3, pulseSize/4, 0, Math.PI * 2);\n                ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7)';\n                ctx.fill();\n            });\n            \n            // 绘制敌人\n            enemies.forEach(enemy => {\n                // 绘制敌人主体\n                ctx.beginPath();\n                ctx.arc(enemy.x, enemy.y, enemy.size, 0, Math.PI * 2);\n                ctx.fillStyle = enemy.color;\n                ctx.fill();\n                \n                // 绘制敌人眼睛\n                ctx.fillStyle = 'white';\n                ctx.beginPath();\n                ctx.arc(enemy.x - enemy.size/3, enemy.y - enemy.size/4, enemy.size/4, 0, Math.PI * 2);\n                ctx.fill();\n                ctx.beginPath();\n                ctx.arc(enemy.x + enemy.size/3, enemy.y - enemy.size/4, enemy.size/4, 0, Math.PI * 2);\n                ctx.fill();\n                \n                // 绘制敌人瞳孔\n                ctx.fillStyle = 'black';\n                ctx.beginPath();\n                ctx.arc(enemy.x - enemy.size/3, enemy.y - enemy.size/4, enemy.size/8, 0, Math.PI * 2);\n                ctx.fill();\n                ctx.beginPath();\n                ctx.arc(enemy.x + enemy.size/3, enemy.y - enemy.size/4, enemy.size/8, 0, Math.PI * 2);\n                ctx.fill();\n            });\n            \n            // 绘制玩家\n            ctx.beginPath();\n            ctx.arc(player.x, player.y, player.size, 0, Math.PI * 2);\n            ctx.fillStyle = player.color;\n            ctx.fill();\n            \n            // 绘制玩家高光\n            ctx.beginPath();\n            ctx.arc(player.x - player.size/3, player.y - player.size/3, player.size/3, 0, Math.PI * 2);\n            ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5)';\n            ctx.fill();\n            \n            // 绘制玩家眼睛\n            ctx.fillStyle = 'white';\n            ctx.beginPath();\n            ctx.arc(player.x - player.size/3, player.y - player.size/6, player.size/4, 0, Math.PI * 2);\n            ctx.fill();\n            ctx.beginPath();\n            ctx.arc(player.x + player.size/3, player.y - player.size/6, player.size/4, 0, Math.PI * 2);\n            ctx.fill();\n            \n            // 绘制玩家瞳孔\n            ctx.fillStyle = '#1a1a2e';\n            ctx.beginPath();\n            ctx.arc(player.x - player.size/3, player.y - player.size/6, player.size/8, 0, Math.PI * 2);\n            ctx.fill();\n            ctx.beginPath();\n            ctx.arc(player.x + player.size/3, player.y - player.size/6, player.size/8, 0, Math.PI * 2);\n            ctx.fill();\n            \n            // 绘制穿墙效果（当玩家靠近边界时）\n            if (player.x < player.size || player.x > CANVAS_WIDTH - player.size ||\n                player.y < player.size || player.y > CANVAS_HEIGHT - player.size) {\n                \n                ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(79, 209, 197, 0.5)';\n                ctx.lineWidth = 2;\n                ctx.setLineDash([5, 5]);\n                ctx.beginPath();\n                ctx.arc(player.x, player.y, player.size + 5, 0, Math.PI * 2);\n                ctx.stroke();\n                ctx.setLineDash([]);\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 游戏循环\n        function gameLoop(currentTime) {\n            const deltaTime = currentTime - lastTime;\n            lastTime = currentTime;\n            \n            update(deltaTime);\n            render();\n            \n            requestAnimationFrame(gameLoop);\n        }\n        \n        // 当页面加载完成后初始化游戏\n        window.onload = init;\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>",
